<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ā bà fù cì gěi wǒ yī shuāng fú yīn xié, píng ān de fú yīn xié.
 chuān shàng tā zǒu chū āi jí bù tíng xiē, zǒu guò nà máng máng de kuàng yě.
 xīn zhōng mǎn le wú bǐ de pàn wàng, mǎn le wú bǐ de xǐ yuè.
 yīn wèi wǒ kàn jiàn le měi lì de jiā nán jiè, měi lì de jiā nán jiè.
 zǒu a zǒu a, chuān shàng fú yīn xié, bǎ zhǒng zi sā biàn tián yě.
 zǒu a zǒu a, chuān shàng fú yīn xié, yīn qín zuò gōng bǎ zhǔ lái yíng jiē.
 yīn qín zuò gōng bǎ zhǔ lái yíng jiē.</lyrics>
<title>chuān shàng fú yīn xié 迦南1147</title>
